#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn5.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn5.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhikkhunīvagga "
msgstr "1. Nuns "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn5.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Uppalavaṇṇāsutta "
msgstr "5. With Uppalavaṇṇā "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.288, sc1
msgctxt "sn5.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.5:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho uppalavaṇṇā bhikkhunī pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā … pe … "
msgstr "Then the nun Uppalavaṇṇā robed up in the morning … "

msgctxt "sn5.5:1.3"
msgid "aññatarasmiṃ supupphitasālarukkhamūle aṭṭhāsi. "
msgstr "and stood at the root of a sal tree in full flower. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.5:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā uppalavaṇṇāya bhikkhuniyā bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo samādhimhā cāvetukāmo yena uppalavaṇṇā bhikkhunī tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā uppalavaṇṇaṃ bhikkhuniṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, wanting to make the nun Uppalavaṇṇā feel fear, terror, and goosebumps, wanting to make her fall away from immersion, went up to her and addressed her in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn5.5:2.1"
msgid "“Supupphitaggaṃ upagamma bhikkhuni, "
msgstr "“You’ve come to this sal tree all crowned with flowers, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:2.2"
msgid "Ekā tuvaṃ tiṭṭhasi sālamūle; "
msgstr "and stand at its root all alone, O nun. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:2.3"
msgid "Na catthi te dutiyā vaṇṇadhātu, "
msgstr "Your beauty is second to none; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:2.4"
msgid "Bāle na tvaṃ bhāyasi dhuttakānan”ti. "
msgstr "silly girl, aren’t you afraid of rascals?” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.132, pts2ed1.289, sc3
msgctxt "sn5.5:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho uppalavaṇṇāya bhikkhuniyā etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then the nun Uppalavaṇṇā thought, "

msgctxt "sn5.5:3.2"
msgid "“ko nu khvāyaṃ manusso vā amanusso vā gāthaṃ bhāsatī”ti? "
msgstr "“Who’s speaking this verse, a human or a non-human?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.5:3.3"
msgid "Atha kho uppalavaṇṇāya bhikkhuniyā etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then she thought, "

msgctxt "sn5.5:3.4"
msgid "“māro kho ayaṃ pāpimā mama bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo samādhimhā cāvetukāmo gāthaṃ bhāsatī”ti. "
msgstr "“This is Māra the Wicked, wanting to make me feel fear, terror, and goosebumps, wanting to make me fall away from immersion!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.5:3.5"
msgid "Atha kho uppalavaṇṇā bhikkhunī “māro ayaṃ pāpimā” iti viditvā māraṃ pāpimantaṃ gāthāhi paccabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Uppalavaṇṇā, knowing that this was Māra the Wicked, replied to him in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn5.5:4.1"
msgid "“Sataṃ sahassānipi dhuttakānaṃ, "
msgstr "“Even if 100,000 rascals like you "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:4.2"
msgid "Idhāgatā tādisakā bhaveyyuṃ; "
msgstr "were to come here, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:4.3"
msgid "Lomaṃ na iñjāmi na santasāmi, "
msgstr "I’d stir not a hair nor panic. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:4.4"
msgid "Na māra bhāyāmi tamekikāpi. "
msgstr "I’m not scared of you, Māra, even alone. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn5.5:5.1"
msgid "Esā antaradhāyāmi, "
msgstr "I’ll vanish, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:5.2"
msgid "kucchiṃ vā pavisāmi te; "
msgstr "or I’ll enter your belly; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:5.3"
msgid "Pakhumantarikāyampi, "
msgstr "I could stand between your eyebrows "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:5.4"
msgid "tiṭṭhantiṃ maṃ na dakkhasi. "
msgstr "and you still wouldn’t see me. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn5.5:6.1"
msgid "Cittasmiṃ vasībhūtāmhi, "
msgstr "I’m the master of my own mind, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:6.2"
msgid "iddhipādā subhāvitā; "
msgstr "I’ve developed the bases of psychic power well. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:6.3"
msgid "Sabbabandhanamuttāmhi, "
msgstr "I’m free from all bonds, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:6.4"
msgid "na taṃ bhāyāmi āvuso”ti. "
msgstr "and I’m not afraid of you, sir!” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.290, sc7
msgctxt "sn5.5:7.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ uppalavaṇṇā bhikkhunī”ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The nun Uppalavaṇṇā knows me!” miserable and sad, vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
